find_library(
    fftw_lib
    names "fftw3"
    paths $env{fftwdir}
    path_suffixes "lib" "lib64"
    no_default_path
  )

find_library(
    fftwf_lib
    names "fftw3f"
    paths $env{fftwdir}
    path_suffixes "lib" "lib64"
    no_default_path
  )

find_library(
    fftwl_lib
    names "fftw3l"
    paths $env{fftwdir}
    path_suffixes "lib" "lib64"
    no_default_path
  )

find_library(gsl_gsl_library
    names libgsl.dll.a gsl libgsl
    paths  ${gsl_possible_root_dirs}
    path_suffixes lib
    doc "gsl library" )

    names libgslcblas.dll.a gslcblas libgslcblas
